a.n: ECE 5 Enfusion Xtreme Standup, Alkmaar, Netherlands

p.d: Enfusion Kickboxing is one of the world’s top Kickboxing organizations. Live events take place all over the world and include Enfusion Live and Enfusion Talent which are both full events of about 2 hours held on the same night. Enfusion represents the highest quality kickboxing in the world, as their shows constantly feature the best and most exciting line-ups possible. The exciting atmosphere, spectacular action and jaw-dropping KO's are the main reason tor the brand's success. Enfusion is a must-see event for all combat sports enthusiasts.
